  <brief_title>Study Evaluating TwoTablet Formulations of Neratinib (HKI-272)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single Dose Bioavailability Study of 2 New Tablet Formulations of Neratinib Compared With a Reference Capsule in Healthy Adult Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
