  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will examine the bioavailability (the rate and extent to which the active
      ingredient or active moiety is absorbed from a drug product and becomes available at the site
      of action) of two tablet formulations of Neratinib (HKI-272) compared to the capsule
      formulation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
